<module>edis_backend</module>
<modulesummary>DB backend behaviour for edis.</modulesummary>
<description>
<p>DB backend behaviour for edis.
  </p><list>
     <item><pre>init(string(), non_neg_integer(), eleveldb:open_options()) -&gt; {ok, ref()} | {error, term()}</pre><p>
       Opens and/or initializes the backend<br/>
     </p></item><item><pre>write(ref(), edis_backend:write_actions()) -&gt; ok | {error, term()}</pre><p>
        Atomically apply a set of actions<br/>
     </p></item><item><pre>put(ref(), binary(), #edis_item{}) -&gt; ok | {error, term()}</pre><p>
       Puts an item in the database<br/>
     </p></item><item><pre>delete(ref(), binary()) -&gt; ok | {error, term()}</pre><p>
       Deletes an item<br/>
     </p></item><item><pre>is_empty(ref()) -&gt; boolean()</pre><p>
       Determines if the database is empty<br/>
     </p></item><item><pre>destroy(ref()) -&gt; ok | {error, term()}</pre><p>
       Deletes database<br/>
     </p></item><item><pre>status(ref()) -&gt; {ok, binary()} | error</pre><p>
       Determines the databse status<br/>
     </p></item><item><pre>get(ref(), binary()) -&gt; #edis_item{} | not_found | {error, term()}</pre><p>
       Gets an item from the database<br/>
     </p></item>
  </list></description>
<section><title>DATA TYPES</title><marker id="types"/>

<taglist>
<tag><c>fold_fun() = (Item::#edis_item{}, any()) -&gt; any()</c></tag>
<item><marker id="type-fold_fun"/> </item>
<tag><c>write_actions() = [{put, Key::binary(), Value::#edis_item{}} | {delete, Key::binary()} | clear]</c></tag>
<item><marker id="type-write_actions"/> </item>
</taglist></section>


